## Beamer

Beamer is an extensive latex class for generating presentation slides. This is
not a full tutorial, just a collection of notes on performing common tasks that
I often forget.

For some guides and tutorials, check out my [delicious tag](http://del.icio.us/yob/r).

### Stopping the irritating default slide animations

Presentations where the dot points appear 1 by 1 drive me nuts.

To disable this behaviour, use the following line before \begin{document}

    \beamerdefaultoverlayspecification{}
